ge_1609594387.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SimonSkafar</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>ONEOK, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKE\" title=\"ONEOK, Inc.\">OKE</a></span>) has a large growth trajectory in the coming year as the firm absorbs the remaining units of EnLink, adds the newly acquired assets from Medallion Midstream to its cash flow, and grows through organic capital</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1609594387/image_1609594387.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742457-oneok-expands-deeper-into-the-oil-pipeline-business", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 01:17:01"}, {"id": "4742456", "title": "Q3 2024 Earnings Insights: Consumer Resilience, AI Advancements And Supply Chain Shifts", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smiling female client shaking hand with businesswoman after meeting at workplace\" data-id=\"1773201817\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Maskot</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>From the Q3 2024 earnings season, there are some important themes emerging from recent earnings calls across various industries. From consumer behavior and technological advances to global market dynamics, these insights reveal how companies are navigating an evolving economic landscape. Below are three</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1773201817/image_1773201817.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742456-q3-24-earnings-insights-consumer-resilience-ai-advancements-and-supply-chain-shifts", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:56:58"}, {"id": "4742459", "title": "Super Micro Computer: Measuring The Risks, Hold For Now", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman using tape measure with risk wording for risk analysis investigate management and assessment concept.\" data-id=\"2150553576\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"822px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dilok Klaisataporn</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The bulls came rampaging back in pre-market trading on December 2nd, 2024 as Super Micro Computer (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>) issued a press release that the independent review of its internal controls, operations, and accounting practices <a href=\"https://ir.supermicro.com/news/news-details/2024/Supermicro-Announces-Completion-of-Review-by-Independent-Special-Committee/default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">has concluded</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2150553576/image_2150553576.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742459-super-micro-computer-smci-measuring-risks-hold-for-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:50:54"}, {"id": "4742453", "title": "Caleres: Margins Are Returning To The Mean As Warned, Still A Hold", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"lots of different shoes stacked in hallway\" data-id=\"82567332\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Martin Poole</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Caleres, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CAL\" title=\"Caleres, Inc.\">CAL</a></span>) presented its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4365344-caleres-non-gaap-eps-of-1_23-misses-0_12-revenue-of-740_94m-misses-10_42m\">Q3 2024 results</a>, which were not bad, with revenues growing on a comparable basis in both the retail and the wholesale branded sector, and operating margins sustained well despite lower absolute</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/82567332/image_82567332.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742453-caleres-margins-are-returning-to-the-mean-as-warned-still-a-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:35:38"}, {"id": "4742448", "title": "UniCredit: Will It Be The Next Leading EU Bank?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Unicredit Tower skyscraper in Milan\" data-id=\"1014081722\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Cineberg</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Here at the Lab, we have good coverage of EU financial institutions. This year, the sector has already delivered a 31% total return, and the banking industry still trades at a 20% discount to long-run P/E multiple and a 47% discount to the broader market. This</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1014081722/image_1014081722.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742448-unicredit-stock-will-it-be-next-leading-eu-bank", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:15:49"}, {"id": "4742445", "title": "Signet: It Has Been Great For Trading, But Not This Time", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stop sign\" data-id=\"157640177\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4368px\" height=\"2912px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NoSystem images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Signet Jewelers Limited</strong> (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIG#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"Signet Jewelers Limited\">SIG</a>), is still a very cheap stock on <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SIG/valuation/metrics?hasComeFromMpArticle=true&amp;source=content_type%253Areact%257Csection%253Amain_content%257Cbutton%253Abody_link\">many valuation measures</a>. In the last year, we have highlighted this name for a swing trade twice successfully. The first a year ago today, which </p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/157640177/image_157640177.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742445-signet-it-has-been-great-for-trading-but-not-this-time", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 00:01:22"}, {"id": "4742442", "title": "Ferrari: Debunking Misconceptions About A Disappointing Third Quarter", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078905514/image_2078905514.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Ferrari SF90 Stradale supercar sports car in showroom, low corner view\" data-id=\"2078905514\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078905514/image_2078905514.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078905514/image_2078905514.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078905514/image_2078905514.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078905514/image_2078905514.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2078905514/image_2078905514.jpg?io=getty-c-w640